Emalunga eliBandla laseWales akhatsatekile ngekufana kweMafutsa
Lamanye emalunga alomkhandlu abekhatsatekile ngekufuna kuguculwa kwesitfunti sawo sibe 'Lilunga lePhalamende yaseWales' (iMWP).
Loku kwabangelwa nguloko lokwakulindzeleke kutsi kuguculwe ligama lalelibandla libe yiPhalamende yaseWales.
Emalunga e-ABC laphuma kuwo onkhe emacembu etepolitiki akhatsatekile ngekutsi kungenteka abe yinhlekisa.
Lilunga lelisebenta ngemandla leliphalamende latsi licembu lakhe likhatsatekile ngoba loku kuyahambisana nemavi latsi "Twp" na "Pwp".
Kulabafundza ema-Welsh, ema-Welsh atsi twp, lokusho kutsi "silly" kantsi ema-Pwp asho kutsi "shit".
Lilunga lePlaid lelicembu lepolitiki latsi lelicembu lonkhe alikeneliswa futsi lacela kutsi kuniketwe emagama lahlukile.
Lilunga le Welsh Conservative Party latsi licembu lakhe "livulekile" ngekuntjintjwa kweligama, kepha waphawula kutsi kunemehluko lomncane emkhatsini weMWP neMapeto.
Kulendzaba, indlela yekuvakalisa leligama le-Welsh w, ifana nendlela yekuvakalisa leligama le-W ku-Yorkshire English.
Likomidi leliphetse lelimiswe ngemalunga elikomidi, lelisebenta ngemtsetfo wekutsi emagama ashintshwe, latsi: Sincumo sekugcina lesimayelana neticu temalunga elikomidi, sitawuletfwa ngemalunga ngekwawo.
Umtsetfo waHulumende waseWales wanga-2017 waniketa Sigungu Sakhamiti emandla ekugucula leligama.
Ngenyanga yeNyoni, lelikomidi lakhipha imiphumela yetinkhulumiswano temphakatsi ngetincomo letaphumela ekusekeleni lokukhulu kwekukhetfwa kwephalamende yase Wales.
Uma kuziwa etigabeni temalunga esishayamtsetfo, lelikomidi lakhetsa emalunga ePhalamende yase Wales nobe i-WMP, kepha i-MWP yatfola kwesekelwa lokukhulu ekuhlolweni kwemphakatsi.
Emalunga aleSigungu kumele kutsi anikete tindlela letitsite, kepha imitamo yekwenta sivumelwano ingabangela tinkinga kuSihlalo, Ellen Jones, lobekancunywe kutsi atawuletsa umtsetfo wekuguculwa kwalomtsetfo emavikini lambalwa.
Umtsetfo Wekuchutjwa Kwemtsetfo utawufaka ekhatsi letinye tingucuko endleleni uMkhandlu weTifundza losebenta ngayo, lokufaka ekhatsi imitsetfo yekukhishwa kwemalunga eMkhandlu kanye neluhlelo lwekucondziswa kwemisebenti.
Emalunga alomhlangano atawutfola litfuba lekugcina lekuvotela emagama awo uma ngabe sekukhulunyiswa ngemtsetfo.
Bantfu baseMacedonia babhunga nge-referendum yekuntjintja ligama lalelive
Bantfu baseNyakatfo ye-Afrika batawuvota ngeLisontfo kutsi bayakwati yini kugucula ligama lalelive libe yi "Republic of North Macedonia".
I-Front National ihlelwe ngemalungiselelo ekucatulula impikiswano yeminyaka leminingi nemakhelwane wayo i-Greece, leseyine sifundza lesibitwa ngekutsi yi-Macedonia.
I-Athena seyinesikhatsi lesidze ichaza kubitwa kwabomakhelwane bayo basenyakatfo ngekutsi kutsatsa indzawo yayo futsi seyiphikisana nemibono yayo ye-EU kanye ne-NATO.
Mengameli waseMacedonia, Giorgi Ivanov, longakemelani nalombono wekutsi leligama le-Macedonia kufanele lishintjwe, utsi angeke awuvume lombono.
Kodvwa-ke, labo labaphakamisa leliviki lekuvota, lokufaka ekhatsi Ndvunankhulu Zoran Zaev, batsi kuguculwa kwalelibizo lelive, kumane nje kuyindleko yekungena e-EU kanye nasesivumelwaneni se-NATO.
Tinkhulumo teSanta Martin tiye taphela njengobe emasontfo aseHarlem alwa kamatima kute aphile
"Bantfu labadzala lengikhulume nabo batsi bekuba netindzawo tekunatsa nemasontfo etindzaweni letisemagunjini", kusho Mnumzane Adams.
Lamuhla kute lalamanye.
Watsi kungabikhona kwaletindzawo tekunatsa tinatfo kuyacondzeka.
"Bantfu sebatiphatsa ngalokwehlukile lamuhla", washo njalo.
 Emabhawa akasuyo imiphakatsi yekuhlala bantfu labaya kuyo njalo.
Ngekubona kwakhe, lisontfo lelingumholi walo, likhatsatekile ngekutsi imali leyakhiwe ngekutsengiswa kwaletakhiwo angeke isachubeka njengobe labaphatsi belibala, futsi kutawufika sikhatsi lapho letakhiwo setitawuphindze tibe khona.
Watsi emasontfo angacitfwa ngemahholwa lanetindlu letinebantfu labangafuni kusita ekulondvoloteni letindzawo letingcwele letisele.
"Bunyenti bebantfu labatawutsenga tindlu kuleto tindlu batawuba ngulabamhlophe", washo, "ngako-ke, kuvalwa kwalamasonto kutawusheshiswa ngobe bantfu labatawutsenga tindlu temakholwa angeke babe ngemalunga alamasontfo".
Omabili lamasonto akha emalunga lamhlophe ngaphambi kwekutsi iHarlem ibe lidolobha lebantfu labamnyama - i-Metropolitan Community - nga 1870, ne St. Martin's Church ngemuva kweminyaka lelishumi.
Umphakatsi wekucala webaholi be Methodist labamhlophe wasuka kulendzawo ngemnyaka wa 1930.
Ummango webaMnyama lebebakhonta edvute wacala kutsatsa lendzawo.
St. Martin's Church yabekwa umtimba webantfu labamnyama, lebebaholi babo kunguMfundisi lomkhulu John Howard Johnson, lobekaphetse umbutsano webatsengisi labasendleleni 125th Street, lokuyindzawo lenkhulu yekutsengisa eHarlem, lebeyicondze kumiswa kwebantfu labamnyama.
Umlilo lowaphuma nga-1939 walimata kakhulu lesakhiwo, kodvwa ngesikhatsi umfundisi longuMfundisi Johnson enta luhlelo lwekulungisa, wacela kutsi kube nemtimba wemculo.
Umfundisi David Johnson, indvodzana ya Johnson kanye nalona lowalandzela uyise eSt Martin's Church, ngekutigcabha wabita le-orchestra ngekutsi "timbila tebasweli".
Lesinye sati lebesikadze sidlala ema-orgel a July satsi lama-orgel "ngumcebo wesintfu" futsi "ayintfo lemcoka lesemlandvweni".
Tiffany Ng, longulomunye wetati temculo wase Michigan, naye waveta kutsi lamagilasi bekungemagilasi ekucala emhlabeni labedlalwa ngumculi lomnyama, Dionisius A. Lind, lowahamba waya emagileni lamakhulu esontfweni laseRiverside eminyakeni lelishumi nesiphohlongo leyendlulile.
Umnumzane Merriweather utsi St. Martin's Church akakamtfoli lomunye longangena esikhundleni sakhe.
Lokwenteka esontfweni iSt. Martin's Church etinyangeni letimbalwa letendlulile kube yintfo lematima leyakhiwe bakhi bemisebenti yemandla kanye neyekusebenta, labanye babo bebatfunywe baholi bemasontfo, labanye batfunywe ngumkhandlu we-Episcopal.
I-Bishop's Administration  Umtimba longamele we-Bishopship, lobunjwe ngebaholi bemasontfo  wabhalela liBhishobishopi ngaJulayi, uvakalisa kukhatsateka ngekutsi liBhishobhozi  litawufuna kuniketa imali yekusebenta kuBhishobhi, nanobe liBhishobhopi belingazange lihlanganyele ekucasheni bakhi betakhiwo kanye nebatsengisi lebebatfunywe liBhishobhi.
Labanye babonisi betifundza bakhala ngelikhono lelisetulu lekubona tintfo ngendlela lecacile.
Umntfwana loneminyaka lelishumi nakutsatfu ubulewe nguleshaka ngesikhatsi idweba tigadla tesiganga eCalifornia
Sikhulu setilwandle sitsi umfana loneminyaka lelishumi nakutsatfu budzala wahlaselwa ngushaka wetimfishi wase California ngesikhatsi kuvalwa lilanga lekuhlanyelwa kwetimfishi.
Kuhlaselwa kwenteka ngaphambi kwensimbi yesikhombisa ekuseni ngase Beacons Beach, Encinitas.
Chad Hammel watjela KSWB-TV eSan Diego kutsi yena nebangani bakhe bebagwedla emanti cishe ihhafu yeli-awa ngaMgcibelo nakava umfana lomncane akhala acela lusito, base bahamba nabo bamyisa emantini bamkhipha.
Hammel utsi wacale wacabanga kutsi bekukukhutsalela kubamba iminenkhe, kepha wabese uyati kutsi bekukhala "Ungigagadzile!"
Ungimemile!
Litsambo lakhe lonkhe lase liyakheke. Hammel watsi watsi nakafika kulomfana wambona.
"Bengicela wonkhe umuntfu kutsi aphume emantini". "Kukhona shark emantini", kwengeta Hammel.
Lomfana wahanjiswa ngemoya longetulu esibhedlela se-Radix lapho simo sakhe besibaluleke kakhulu.
Akwatiwa kutsi ngukuphi lokuhlasela lokwentiwe ngulemfishi.
Sikhulu sebasebenti beLwandle Larry Giles, sitjele bemitfombo yetindzaba kutsi le shark yayikadze ibonwa kulendzawo emasontfo lambalwa ekucaleni, kepha kwatfolwa kutsi ayisiyo lephako.
Giles uphindze watsi lomuntfu lobulale uhlatjwe tinhlavu letibuhlungu kakhulu.
Baphatsi bavale imigwaco kusukela ePonto Beach eCasablad kuya eSwamix Beach e-Ecinitas, sikhatsi lesingaba ngema-awa langu-48 ngenca yekuphenya kanye nekuvikela.
Giles utsi kunetinhlobo letingetulu kwa-135 te-shark letitfolakala kulendzawo, kodvwa linyenti lato atikabonakali tingoti.
iSainsbury's ihlela kungena emakethe yebuhlakani yaseBrithani
iSainsbury's iba ngumncintiswano nemakheya lafaka ekhatsi iBoots, Superdrug kanye ne Debenhams kanye nemikhakha yetitjalo tekuhlobisa leyenta kutsi labosita labasebenta ngekuhlobisa basebentise indlela yekuhlobisa.
Njengencenye yekungena kwemakethe yebuntfu yaseBrithani leyenta tigidzi temarandi letingu 2,8, lekhulako kantsi futsi nekutsengiswa kwemikhicito yemfashini kanye nekutsengiswa kwetintfo tasekhaya kuyehla, tigaba letinkhulu tetitfo tebuciko butawuhlolwa etitolo letilishumi nakunye eveni lonkhe, futsi titakwandvwa tibe ngetulu kwetitolo letinyenti ngemnyaka lotako nangabe tiphumelela.
Kungobe emasuphamakethe atfola tindlela tekusebentisa emashelufu labekadze asetjentiselwa ema-TV, ema-microwave kanye nemishini yasendlini.
Sainsbury's utsi itawuphindza kabili linani letintfo tekutihlobisa ngekutsi iletse imikhicito lengetulu kwa-3000, lefaka ekhatsi imikhicito yemikhicito lefana ne Revlon, Essie, Tweezerman kanye na Dr. PawPaw kwekucala ngca.
Tintfo letisetjentiswa ku-L'Oreal, Maybelline kanye ne-Burt's Bees titawuphindze titfole indzawo etincenyeni letifanana naleto letitfolakala etitolo letifana neBoots.
Le supermarket itawuphindze ivule kabusha i-boutique makeup line yayo ngekutsi liningi laletintfo litoyiba letisebentako kubantfu labamnyama - intfo lefunwa kakhulu ngulabadzala.
Ngetulu kwaloko, sitolo setinongo iFragrance Shop sitawuhlola tindzawo tekutsengisa etitolo letimbili te-Sainsbury, lesinye saletitolo sivulwe e-Croydon, eningizimu yeLondon, kuleliviki leliphelile, kantsi lesinye sitawuhlelwa e-Selly Oak, eBirmingham, ngekuhamba kwesikhatsi kulomnyaka.
Kutsenga ku-inthanethi kanye nekutfutsela ekutsengeni kudla lokuncane lokwentiwa onkhe malanga etitolo tekudla letisedvute kusho kutsi bosomabhizinisi kumele basebente kamatima kukhanga bantfu kutsi bete.
Mike Coupe, umengameli weSainsbury's, utsi, "Lokucuketfwe ngekusebenta njengetindzawo tekutsengisela, njengetindlela tekutsengiswa letitfutfukako tekulwa nemikhicito leminingi ye-Aldi ne-Lidl, lekuniketwa ngetinsita letinyenti kanye nemikhicito lengasilo yekudla".
ISainsbury's ivule emahhovisi e-Argos etitolo tayo letitsengisa kudla emakhulwini etitolo, futsi iphindze yavula emahhovisi e-Habitat kusukela yatsenga lamahhovisi eminyakeni lemibili leyengcile, lokusho kutsi kukhuliswe kutsengiswa kwemikhicito yekudla kanye nekutfola imali.
Kwatsi nje umshikashika wekwenta kabusha tikhungo temitsi kanye nemitsi wahambela etulu.
I-Sainsbury's yacala budlelwano ne-Boots chain ekucaleni kwa-2000 kepha budlelwano babo baphela ngekungevani mayelana nekwabelana ngemali lekhokhwa ngemakhemisi etitolo tabo.
Lisu lelisha lacala ngemuva kwekutsi iSainsbury's itsengise emakethe yayo yema-pharmacy langu-281 eminyakeni lemitsatfu leyengcile ku-Celesio, umnikati we-Lloyd's Pharmacy, ngemali lengema-£125 million.
Kutsiwa iLloyds itawuba nendzima kuloluhlelo ngekutsi ngetitolo letine, ifake leminye imikhicito yetintfo tekunakekelwa kwesikhumba, kufaka ekhatsi iLa Roche-Posay neVichy.
Paul Mills-Hicks, umcondzisi wetekutsengiswa kwetintfo we Sainsbury's, utsi: "Sihle sitintjintje kubukeka nekusetjentiswa kwetintfo tebuhlakani betfu kute sinikete emakhasimende etfu indzawo lenhle.
Sinebacashi labaceceshiwe labatawusita ngekweluleka.
Luhlu lwetintfo letitsengiswako luye lwatfutfukiswa kute luhlangabetane netidzingo tabo bonkhe, futsi indzawo yetfu lenhle kanye nendzawo yetfu lesemkhatsini kusho kutsi nyalo sesibantfu labafuna kuhamba etindzaweni letitsite kute siyewubuka buhle betfu lobusendzaweni lobusenta kutsi sibeke imitsetfo leyehlukile kunendlela yetfu yasendvulo yekutsenga.
Peter Jones utfukutsele kakhulu ngemuva kwekukhipha kwaHolly Willoughby kusivumelwano sakhe semali lengu-R11 million
Umdlali we Dragons Den, Peter Jones, ujabulile ngemuva kwekutsi umengameli weTV, Holly Willoughby, akhiphe isivumelwano sakhe semali-yane letigidzi leti-11 tetinkhundla kute agcizelele umsebenti wakhe we-Marks and Spencer kanye ne-ITV.
Willoughby ute sikhatsi sekwenta tintfo takhe tekutiphilisa kanye netintfo takhe tekutilungisa.
Lenkampani yalabashadikazi beyenta kufaniswa ne Goop brand kanye ne Gwyneth Paltrow.
Umsakati we This Morning, 37, ukhiphe umlayeto we-Instagram, wekutsi sewutawuyekela lomsebenti.
Holly Willoughby ucansula inkanyezi ye Dragons' Den Peter Jones ngekutsatsa umhlalaphansi emnyakeni wabo lomuhle wekukhangisa  kute agcile kumiklomelo yakhe lensha yemali leyakhiwe ngemafemu lafaka ekhatsi iMarks & Spencer ne-ITV.
Imimango itsi Jones bekatfuke kakhulu ngesikhatsi lentfombi leyayimphuya yemsakato yemukela, ngesikhatsi semhlangano lebeyimatasatasa ngeLesibili, ehhovisi lelisetulu lelibhizinisi lakhe eMarlow, Buckinghamshire, kutsi tinkhontileka takhe letinsha, letingaba yimali lengange-R1.50 million, kusho kutsi besekangeke asaba nesikhatsi sekusebenta ngelikhaya lakhe kanye netintfo takhe letisezingeni lelisetulu i-Truly.
Le nkampani yafaniswa ne Gwyneth Paltrow Goop futsi bekubikelwa kutsi itawuphindza kabili umcebo wa Willoughby locatjangwa kutsi ufinyelela ku-R11 million.
Ngesikhatsi Willoughby, lobekaneminyaka lengu-37 budzala, aveta ngalokusemtsetfweni ku-Instagram kutsi sewuyahamba, Jones wahamba ngemkhumbi wasuka eBrithani waya kulenye indzawo lapho bekahlala khona.
Umtfombo utsi: "Holly ubeke Truly etulu kwetintfo letibalulekile".
Bekuhlela sikhatsi lesidze, bekutawucinisekisa kutsi utfola imali lengenako ngeminyaka leminyenti lelandzelako.
Sincumo sakhe sekutiyekela sakhatsateka kakhulu.
Kute lowakholwa kutsi kwentekani ngalesibili, besekusondzele kakhulu.
Endlunkhulu yaseMarlow, kunelithende leligcwele tintfo letilungele kutsengiswa.
Lucwalingo lukhombisa kutsi kushiya kwakhe lomsakati we-This Morning, losemkhatsini wetinkanyezi letisezingeni lelikhulu e-UK, kungadla imali lenyenti kulelibhizinisi ngenca yemali layitsetse ekwakhiweni kwetintfo letinsha, kusuka kumamashiyane nemakhandlela, timphahla kanye netintfo tasendlini, kanye nekungeta kwesikhatsi sekusungula.
Loku kungaphindze kusho kuphela kwebungani lobudze.
Make wa-Willoughby webantfwana labatsatfu kanye nendvodza yakhe Dan Baldwin, bebasondzelene na-Jones kanye nemkakhe, Tara Capp, iminyaka lelishumi.
Willoughby wasungula iTruly na Capp nga 2016, Jones, 52, wajoyina nga March njengemcondzisi wale nkampani.
Labashadene baya eholidini ndzawonye futsi Jones uhlanganyela ku-40% we-Balduin Productions.
Willoughby utawuba ngummeli we-M&S futsi utawutsatsa sikhundla sa-Anta McPartlin njengenhloko ye-ITV show I'm A Celebrity.
Umtfombo losondzelene naJones ubike ngalokwentekile ebusuku. "Asikhulumi ngemabhizinisi akhe".
