Kutamatama kwemhlaba ne tsunami e-Indonesia kwabhubhisa le-Island, kwabulala emakhulu ebantfu
Kwatsi ngemuva kwekutamatama kwemhlaba e-Lombok Island, ema-NGO lavela emaveni angaphandle atjelwa kutsi lusito lwawo aludzingeki.
Nanobe bantfu labangetulu kwa-10 ekhulwini base-Lombok batfutseliwe, kute simo lesibucayi lesake samenyetelwa, lokungumgomo wekucela lusito lwemave emhlaba.
"Kulihlazo kutsi etikhatsini letinyenti, baye bakwenta kwacaca kutsi abafuni lusito lwelive, ngako-ke kutawuba matima", kwasho Make Sumbung.
Njengobe i-Save the Children ibeka licembu lelitawuya ePala, solo abakanati kutsi basebenti bangaphandle bangakhona yini kusebenta endzaweni.
Umkhulumeli we-NDA, M. Sutopo, utsi, tikhulu tase-Indonesia tihlolisisa simo sasePalu kute titfole kutsi ngabe kufanele yini kutsi ema-ejensi emave emhlaba avumelekile kutsi abe nencenye ekusiteni.
Ngekubona kutamatama kwemhlaba lokwenteka njalo e-Indonesia, kuyadzabukisa kutsi lelive alitilungiselelanga kahle tintfo temvelo.
Nanobe takhiwo tekukhosela ema-tsunami takhiwa e-Aceh, atikavami kubonwa kuletinye tincenye te-coast.
Kubikwa kutsi kute tsunami lowawukhona esigodzini sasePalau, ngisho nobe bekunecwayiso sekutsi kutawufika tsunami, kodvwa loko kwabangela kutsi kube nekufa lokukhulu.
Kuletinye tiqhingi tase-Indonesia, kuhamba kuyinsayeya.
Tehlakalo temvelo tenta kube matima kakhulu kulawula tintfo letidzingekako.
Sikebhe semaphoyisa lasemkhatsini ne Lombok, lesita kulabantfu labashone kulokudvuma, sesisendleleni leya ePaula, kepha kutawutsatsa emalanga lamatsatfu kutsi sifike endzaweni lapho kuvele khona lesinye sehlakalo.
Mengameli Joko Widodo, umkhankhaso wakhe wekukhetfwa kweliphalamende wawubuke kakhulu ekulungiseni takhiwonchanti tase-Indonesia, futsi akazange akhokhe imali yetindlela kanye netinsimbi.
Kodvwa, kuswelakala kwemitfombolusito kubangele kutsi hulumende waMnu. Jokoc abhekane nelusizi lolukhulu njengobe alindzeleke kutsi alungise lolukhetfo lolusha lolutakwenteka ngemnyaka lotako.
Umnumzane Joko uphindze abe sengotini yekubhekana nekungevani lokungapheli emkhatsini wemacembu ase-Indonesia lapho khona emalunga emalunga ema-Muslim lamanyenti emukela indlela yekukholwa leyesekelako.
Bantfu labangetulu kwe-1 000 balahlekelwa timphilo tabo futsi tinkhulungwane tebantfu tahlatjelwa ngenca yekulwa emigwacweni kwemacembu emaKrestu nemaSulumane, asebentisa imimese, butjoki kanye nemimese kanye naletinye tikhali letisembili.
Buka: Umdlali weLiverpool, Daniel Sturridge, ushaye ligoli lelisindzako lelisusa bhola lelibekelwe iChelsea.
Daniel Sturridge uvikele iLiverpool ekulahlekelweni yi-Premier League ngekushaya igoli ngemzuzu wamashumi lasiphohlongo nemfica ngeMgcibelo e-Stamford Bridge, eLondon.
