Njengobe bekulindzelekile, i-Hurricane Rosa beseyinciphisile emandla ayo ngekuhamba emantini labandzako lasenyakatfo yeLwandle lwaseMexico.
Kodvwa, ngekuhamba kwesikhatsi, lesiphepho lesibitwa ngekutsi nguRosa sitawubangela tikhukhula eveni lonkhe lelingasenyakatfo yeMexico kanye naseningizimu-nshonalanga yeMelika.
Sichotho se-Rosina, lesasichachachate kakhulu, besivakale singemamayela langu-185 ngehora kusukela nga-5 ekuseni ngeLisontfo, ngesikhatsi seMphumalanga, futsi besikhashane ngemamayela langu-385 eningizimu-nshona yePunta Eugenia, eMexico.
Rosa bekabhekene netimo letimatima, bekalindzeleke kutsi aye enyakatfo ngeLisontfo.
Njengobe Sikhatsi Lesinemkhatsi (Tropical Storm) Rosa sisondzela ngaseningizimu-ntshonalanga ye-Baja California Peninsula ngeMsombuluko, itawucala kususa umoya loshisako ngasenyakatfo-ningizimu ye-United States.
Kutawutsi ngeMsombuluko, Rosa aletse imvula lengemashumi etintsatfu nemasentimitha etinhlangeni letiseMexico.
Lomswakama loshisako lochamuka endzaweni leshisako lotawube uhlangene nemoya loshisako lotawube usakha imvula lenkhulu eningizimu nshonalanga emalangeni letako.
Kuletinye tindzawo, 1 kuya ku-4 wetintshi temvula letawuba nemiphumela leminingi lefana netikhukhula, tikhukhula kanye nemihelo yemhlaba.
Sulube lolukhulu lolutfutfukako lutawukwenta kubete imvula lekhona emkhatsini wema-intshi lamabili kuya kulamatsatfu ngelihora, ikakhulu etigodzini letiseNingizimu yeNevada nase-Arizona.
Kwetfulwa kwemvula lengaba ngu 2 kuya ku 4 intshi emimangweni leseningizimu nshonalanga, ikakhulu endzaweni lenkhulu yase Arizona.
Tikhukhula tingaba khona ngenca yesimo selitulu lesibi kakhulu kanye nemvula lenkhulu.
Kuhamba ngetinyawo kuya ehlane bekungaba yintfo lengakacatjangelwa, ngetulu kwetingoti letivela emvuleni.
Tikhukhula temanti tingabangela imifula leme ngendlela lengakafaneli, lokwenta kutsi kube nemimoya leshisako kanye nesivunguvungu.
Lendzawo leseyomile itakwetfula tikhala letinkhulu letitawubangela tikhukhula letincane letitawufika kuletinye tindzawo letiseceleni kwelwandle lwase Southern California.
Kungenteka kutsi kube nekwehla kwemanti lokungetulu kwelihhafu ye-intshi, lokungabangela kuncipha kwetigodzi kanye nemabhudvu.
Loku kutawuba yimvula yekucala kulesigodzi.
Sikhatsi sekwehla kwemvula lenkhulu lesiningi lesitawufika e-Arizona ngeLisontfo ekuseni bese kuba nguMsombuluko ekuseni, ngaphambi kwekutsi litulu libe liningi ngeLisontfo naLesibili.
Tintfo letiphangisako titawufika e Four Corners ngaLesibili bese tichubeka ngeLesitsatfu.
Nga Okthoba, simo selitulu singaba nemoya losetulu eMelika yonkhe njengoba iArctic iba nguleyo lepholile bese emaTropics ahlala asashisa.
Ngalesinye sikhatsi loku kuletsa kushisa lokukhulu ngekushesha.
Sibonelo lesihle kakhulu sekwehluka kwetimo telitulu eMelika leseNshonalanga ngeLisontfo.
Kushisa lokukhulu kwaKansas City, Missouri, Omaha, Nebraska, kanye nekushisa lokukhulu kwaSt. Louis kanye neDes Moines, Iowa, bekungaba ngu-20°C.
Kulamalanga lambalwa lalandzelako, lokushisa kwehlobo lokusele kutozama kuphindze kutfobe bese kuyanda.
Kusuka enyangeni ya Okthoba kutawuba nemoya loshisako etigodzini letisemkhatsini kanye nasemphumalanga yelive laseMelika, lokushisa lokungaba ngu 80° kusuka kumhlaba loseningizimu kuya etincenyeni letisemnyakatfo-mpumalanga.
Kushisa kakhulu nyalo e-New York City, lokungafika ku-80°C ngeLesibili, lokungaba ngu-10°C ngetulu kwesilinganiso.
Sikhatsi lesidze semkhatsi sikhomba simo selitulu lesingetulu kwesilinganiso eNyakatfo Melika naseMpumalanga yeMelika emkhatsini wenyanga yeMphala.
