Lona ngumuti lapho kuhlala khona bantfu labanyenti labangemaTurkish ngaphandle kwaseTurkey.
Emaphoyisa akhulume ngetindlela tekuphepha njengesizatfu sekuvimba umhlangano webantfu labangu 25 000 ngaphandle kwemaswati, kepha bantfu labanyenti bebatseleke ngekutimisela edvute nabo kute babonane nemengameli wabo.
Emakhulu ebabhikishi labamelana na-Erdogan - labanyenti babo labangemaKurd - nabo bebakhuluma kakhulu, bagceka timiso ta-Erdogan kanye nesincumo sahulumende wase-Germany sekumemukela kulelive.
Kuvala kwalemibhikisho lemibili kuveta kwehlukana kwemibono mayelana nalomvakashi, lobukelelwa ngemaJalimane lamaTurkey njenglihlahlandlela, abe aphikiswa ngulabanye ngekuba ngumbusi.
