Sikhohlakali Rosa usongela kumosha iPhoenix, Las Vegas, iSalt Lake City (lokungaba lusito etindzaweni letishaywe somiso)
Kuvamile kutsi tiphepho letinemandla tihlasele i-Arizona, kepha nguloko lokutawenteka esikhatsini lesincane nje evikini lelitako njengoba iSiphepho i-Rosa, lesisalele, sihlasela i-desert lese ningizimu nshonalanga, siletsa ingoti yekukhukhula.
I-National Weather Service seyikhiphe tecwayiso tetikhukhula ngeMsombuluko nangeLesibili e-Western Arizona kanye nase-Southern kanye nase-Eastern Nevada, eSouth-Eastern California nase-Utah, kufaka ekhatsi i-Phoenix, i-Las Vegas kanye ne-Salt Lake City.
Lizulu le Rosa litawugucuka licondze ngase Phoenix ngaLesibili, bese kutsi litawugcwala ngeMsombuluko ebusuku.
Sikhungo setemvelo sasePhoenix, e-Phoenix National Weather Service, sabhala ku-Twitter kutsi, "Kusukela nga-1950, kunetimphepho letingu-10 letatitsetse sikhundla setiphepho noma tiphepho letincane letimbalwa ngemakhilomitha langu-200 e-Phoenix".
Katrina (1967) bekusiphepho lebesikadze sisemkhatsini wemakhilomitha langu-40 nemakhilomitha langu-50 kusuka e-Arizona.
Sikhatsi lesifisha lesikhombisako lesisuka kuSikhungo Savelonkhe Setiphepho sicabanga kutsi litulu litawutfola ku 2 kuya ku 4 wemasentimitha, bese etindzaweni letingaphansi kwe Mogollon Rim eArizona kufika ku 6 wemasentimitha.
Kuletinye tindzawo letisemphumalanga lese ningizimu, kufaka ekhatsi indzawo lesemkhatsini weRockies kanye ne Great Basin, kungahle kube ngu 1 kuya ku 2 intshi, kantsi kungahle kube ngu 4 intshi etindzaweni letisele.
Etindzaweni letingavikeleki emanti, imvula yeRosina ingaba sibusiso ngobe lendzawo igcwele somiso.
Nanobe tikhukhula tibe yinkinga lenkhulu, incenye yaletindzawo letishisako kungenteka kutsi tibe lusito ngobe eningizimu nshonalanga manje seyinesomiso.
Ngekusho kwe-U.S. Drought Management Agency, emaphesenti langetulu kwa-40 e-Arizona, sekanesomiso lesikhulu, lesibili ngetulu, kubika i-weather.com.
I-Hurricane Rosa itawucala kuhamba iye endzaweni lesandingilizi lese-Baja California lese-Mexico.
I-Rosa, lesebentisa emandla esimo se-hurricane, ngeLisontfo ekuseni, itawube inemoya lonemandla lamakhulu lamashumi lasiphohlongo nemfica emahora, itawube ingemakhilomitha lamakhulu lasiphohlongo kuya kumakhulu lamatsatfu nesiphohlongo eningizimu yePunta Eugenia, eMexico, ihamba ngesivinini lesimashumi lamabili emahora.
