Tikhukhula temanti letisendzaweni yase Mexico tingaba nemandla kakhulu futsi tingenta kube netikhukhula letinkhulu.
"Imvula lenkhulu yemvula leyayingemayintshi lamatsatfu kuya kulasitfupha beyingahle isuke eBaja California iye eNyakatfo Nshonalanga yase Sonora, futsi kungenteka ifike ku-10", kubika i-weather.com.
I-Rosa itotsintseka enyakatfo ite yehlele eMexico njengesiphepho lesinemandla ngaphambi kwekufika e-Arizona ekuseni ngaLesibili njengesitfwatfwa lesinemandla lesitawufika e-Arizona nase ningizimu ye-Utah ebusuku ngaLesibili.
