Emakhulu alahlekelwe timphilo tawo ngekutamatama kwemhlaba kanye nasetsunami e-Indonesia, futsi lelinani lisachubeka nekukhula
Bese kushone bantfu labangu 384, labanyenti babo babulawa ngulelifu lelikhulu lelakhukhula emagagasi labese agubha emabhishi ngesikhatsi kutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu kanye ne tsunami kugadla esihlengeni sase Sulawesi, kusho tiphatsimandla ngeMgcibelo.
Emakhulukhulu ebantfu abehlangene elugwini loludvutane nelidolobha iPalu ngaLesihlanu ngesikhatsi emagagasi lanemamitha lasitfupha kuya etulu (18 feet) ashaya elugwini kusihlwa, abulala bantfu labanyenti futsi abhidlita konkhe lokwakungene endleleni.
Kutseleke kutamatama kwemhlaba lokungu-7.5.
"Ngesikhatsi kushiwo kutsi kunetinkhomba tekutsi kunema-tsunami, bantfu bebasolo benta imisebenti yabo ebhishi futsi abazange bashiye emakhaya, ngako-ke babulawa", kusho Sutopo Purwo Nugroho, lomkhulumeli we-Indonesian Disaster Management Agency, akhuluma eJakarta.
"Litsunami alizange lifike lodwa, lalifaka netimoto, emabhuluko, tindlu, lahlasela umhlaba wonkhe", kusho Nugroho, wachubeka watsi letsunami yahamba ngelwandle ngesivinini lesingemakhilomitha la-800 ngelihora ngaphambi kwekutsi ishaye.
Watsi labanye bantfu bakhona kugibela tihlahla futsi baphila.
Bantfu labangu 16,700 bakhululwe etindzaweni letilishumi nambili e-Palu.
Titfombe letibukwa etulu letikhishwe ngulelitiko lelisebenta ngetiphepho tikhombisa tindzawo letinyenti letishayelwe phansi, emabhuloho labhidvukile kanye nemasontfo lageletwe ngemanti.
Kuntenteka kwemhlaba lokuchubekako kwachubeka ngeMgcibelo edolobheni leliselwandle.
Tamatamave latigadla tinekhatsi letinkhulu.
I-Indonesia's Technology Assessment and Application Agency (BPPT) isho esitatimendeni kutsi emandla ekutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu lokwenteka ngaLesihlanu, bekuphindvwe ka-200 kunalawo asebhombu ye atomic leyasetjentiswa e-Hiroshima ngesikhatsi semphi yemhlaba yesibili.
Kungenteka kutsi indzawo yaleli dolobha, lebeyisekhatsi kwemfula lomncane, yenta le tsunami yaba nemandla kakhulu.
I-Nugroho ichaza lomonakalo njengaloyo lomkhulu kakhulu, watsi tinkhulungwane temakhaya, tibhedlela, tindzawo tekutsengisa kanye nema-hotel abhidlitwa.
Watsi imitimba yalabagwaziwa itfolwe ngaphansi kwetakhiwo letishayekile, kwatsiwa bantfu labangu 540 balimele kantsi labangu 29 bayanyamalala.
Ngekuya kwalesikhatsi, bantfu labanyenti bebangabanjwa ngulesihlakalo, kantsi labanye bebangabanjwa ngulesihlakalo.
Imibiko "yayicedziwe ngalokuphelele" ngaphandle kwemibiko levela e-Donggale, kusho Nugroho.
"Bantfu labangetulu kwa-300 000 bahlala kulendzawo", kusho i-Red Cross esitatimendeni, yengeta kutsi basebenti bayo kanye nemavolontiya basendleleni leya etindzaweni letishayekile.
"Loku vele kuyintfo lembi, kodvwa kunetintfo letingaba timbi kakhulu", kwasho bona.
NgaloMgcibelo, lelitiko labekwa licala ngekungabikho kwembiko wekutamatama kwemhlaba ePhala, nomanje tiphatsimandla titsi lemisindvo yafika ngesikhatsi lesifanele.
Imibhalo lemincane leyatsatselwa bantfu emmangweni, ikhombisa indvodza lesitezi lesisetulu, lelayisha bantfu labasetitaladini ngephansi kwayo, icwayisa nge tsunami leyetako.
Ngemuva kwemizuzu lembalwa, lamanti lachamuka lapho atfwesa tindlu kanye nemoto.
I-Reuters beyingakhoni kucinisekisa kutsi loluciko lwekucocisana belungu.
