I-United States kufanele iphindvwe kabili lemali lekhelwa i-AI
Njengobe iChina iba nemandla kakhulu ekuhloleni buhlakani bebuhlakani lobungasibo, iUnited States kufanele iphindvwe kabili imali lesetjentiswa ekuhloleni lobuhlakani, kusho Kai-Fu Lee, longumcambi kanye nemuntfu lowenta buhlakani bebuhlakani lobungasibo, lobekasebentela iGoogle, iMicrosoft kanye neApple.
Lamavi avela ngemuva kwekutsi tikhungo letehlukene tembuso waseMelika tikhiphe imilayeto lemayelana nebuhlakani bekucala, nanobe iMelika ingakabi nelicebo lelisemtsetfweni mayelana nebuhlakani bekucala.
Kwanyalo, ngemnyaka lophelile, iChina ikhiphe licebo layo: licebo lekutsi ibe yintfo yekucala embonweni webuhlakani lobungemajaha nga 2030.
"Kuphindvwa kabili kwebhajethi yebuhlakani bekungenta sicalo lesikahle, uma sicabanga kutsi onkhe lamanye emave asemuva kakhulu kunaseMelika, futsi sifuna kuphumelela lokusha kwebuhlakani bekucondzisisa", kusho Lee.
Kucedza kusebenta kwemabhizinisi lamasha, kwenta kutsi kube lula kutsi emabhizinisi lasembili aseMelika akhiphe imali lengetulu.
Lee, lobhala incwadzi letsi "Superpowers of Artificial Intelligence: China, Silicon Valley and the New World Order" leyashicilelwa ngumshicileli iHoughton Mifflin Harcourt kule nyanga, ungumphatsi we-Synovation Ventures, leye yatsenga kuyinye yetinkampani te-AI letatiwako tase-China, i-Face++.
Wabese ucitsa iminyaka leminyenti ku Carnegie Mellon University, asebenta nge-AI lekhombisa kutsi incono kune-Othello, umculi waseMelika, ngekuhamba kwesikhatsi waba ngumcondzisi we-Microsoft Research kanye nemengameli we-Google e-China.
Lee wahlonipha imincintiswano yasendvulo yahulumende wemateknoloji lefana ne-Robotics Challenge ye-Agency for Advanced Defense Research Projects, wabuta kutsi balungiselela nini umncintiswano lolandzelako lapho khona labatawuveta imibono yabo.
Lee utsi bacwaningi baseMelika bahlangabetana netinkinga letinkhulu tekutfola imali yahulumende.
"I-China ayisihluphi ngebaholi betfu etikolweni, yintfo leyentiwa tinkapani", Lee washo njalo.
Kuleminyaka leyengcile, iFacebook, iGoogle kanye naletinye tinkampani tebucwepheshe ticale kucasha bantfu labatiwako labasuka emanyuvesi kute basebente ngekuhlakanipha lokufakako.
Lee watsi kuguculwa kwemtsetfo wekungenisa bantfu eveni kungasita iUnited States kutsi ihlanganise imitamo yayo kubuhlakani lobukhicitako.
"Ngicabanga kutsi kufanele kuniketwe ngemakhadi laluhlata ngekutimela kubafundzi labane-PhD labati tinhlelo tebuhlakani bekwenta", kwasho yena.
I-State Council yase-China ikhiphe luhlelo lwayo lwekwenta buhlakani lobusha be-AI nga-Julayi 2017.
LiTiko laVelonkhe leTemasayensi yeMvelo likhokhela bantfu etikhungweni temfundvo ngendlela lefanako naleyo i-National Science Foundation kanye naletinye tinhlangano tahulumende letiniketa imali kubacwaningi baseMelika, kodvwa lizinga lemfundvo lephakeme lihle kakhulu eChina, kusho Lee.
Ekucaleni kwalomnyaka e-United States, Litiko Letekuvikela lasungula Sikhungo Sekuhlanganyela sebuCwepheshe beBukrelethi lofuna kufaka ekhatsi balingani labasemsebentini kanye netemfundvo, kantsi neNdlu yeLusebungu (White House) yatsi isungula Likomidi leKukhetsa i-Artificial Intelligence.
Kule nyanga, iDARPA imemetele kusisa tigidzigidzi letimbili temadola ku-initiative lebitwa ngekutsi yi-AI Next.
Kantsi, kulesikhatsi, i-National Science Foundation, nyalo seyitfutsele imali lengetulu kwetigidzi temadola ngemnyaka ekucwaningeni ngebuhlakani lobungemanga.
Kwanyalo, umtsetfo waseMelika lobewufuna kwakha iKhomishana yeKuphepha kweSive ngeBuhlakani beBuciko (i-AI) tinyanga letinyenti awukenti lutfo.
