"Ngifike lamuhla kutovota likusasa lelive, lelive lebantfu labasha baseMacedonia, kute baphile bakhululekile esiveni semave aseYurophu ngoba loko kusho imphilo lephephile kitsi sonkhe", kusho Oliver Georgijevska, lobekaneminyaka lengemashumi lasikhombisa nakune budzala, ngesikhatsi aseSkoplje.
Nanobe kungakabekelwa, linyenti lemalunga ePhalamende litsi litawuvumelana nalokushicilelwe futsi liphindze litsi loko lokwentiwe kutawutsatsa sincumo.
