LiKomiti leluKhetfo laVelonkhe litsi kute imibiko levelako mayelana nalomsebenti lobangelwe ngulelicembu letembusave kusukela ngalelinye lilanga kuya kulelinye lilanga ngelilanga lelishumi nakubili.
Kodvwa-ke, loku bekungemaphesenti la-16 kuphela, nakucatsaniswa na 34% walenombolo yelinyenti leyakhetfwa elukhetfweni lwanga 2016 lapho khona 66% walenombolo yebavoti bavota.
