Ndvunankhulu waseMasedoniya Zoran Zaev, umkakhe Zorica kanye nendvodzana yakhe Dusko bavota ku-referendum yaseMasedoniya yekuguculwa kweligama, lebeyingase ivule indlela yabo yekuba lilunga le-NATO kanye ne-European Union, e-Strumica, eMacedonia, mhlaka 30 Inyoni 2018.
Ngaphandle kweliphalamende laseSkopje, Vladimir Kavardarkov (54) ulungise libutfo lelincane futsi wahudvula titulo ethendeni lelakhiwe ngulabo labangafuni kuvota.
"Sisembili kwe NATO kanye ne EU, kepha sifuna kungenela ngekuphakamisa tinhloko, hhayi ngemnyango wangemuva", kusho Kavadarkov.
Sive lesesiphuyile, kodvwa lesiligugu.
Uma bangafuni kutsi semukelwe njengeMasedoniya, singaya kulamanye emave lafana neChina neRussia, bese siba yincenye yemphakatsi wase Eurasia.
Ndvunankhulu Zaev utsi kuba lilunga le-NATO kutawuletsa lutjalotimali letilindzelekile eMasedonia lapho lizinga lekungasebenti lingetulu kwa-20%.
"Nginelitsemba lekutsi linyenti litawuphikisa loku ngobe ngetulu kwa 80% webantfu bakitsi bakhetsa i-EU ne-NATO", kusho Zaev ngemuva kwekubeka lamakhasi.
