Emkhatsini welive lase Bolivia, kusekhona inkhumbulo lecinile yaloluguya lolwalahlekela eChile ngekulwa lokwaba yingati ngeminyaka yandvulo yelishumi nemfica, kanye nelitsemba lekuphindze atfole iPacific Ocean.
Letetsemba tingahle tibe nguletinkhulu kakhulu eminyakeni leminingi leyendlulile ngalesikhatsi iBolivia ilindzele sincumo seNkantolo Yemave Emhlaba nga-Okthoba 1, ngemuva kweminyaka lesihlanu yemkhandlu.
"Bolivia seyivele ikhona, ngendlela yekuhlangana kanye nekuthula, futsi ngekwemibono, ilindzele umphumela lomuhle", kusho Roberto Calzadilla, umdiplomat waseBolivia.
Bantfu labanyenti baseBolivia batawubona lesincumo seNkantolo Yemave Emhlaba ngekubuka titfombe letikhulukati letitfolakala etindzaweni letehlukahlukene kulelive, betsemba kutsi inkantolo yaseHague itawuniketa sincumo lesitawusekela i-Bolivia, futsi sicinisekise kutsi  ngemuva kwemashumi eminyaka yekungcocisana lokuyinkinga  iChile kumele ivumelane netincociswano tekuniketa i-Bolivia indlela lephumako leya elwandle.
Evo Morales, umengameli waseBolivia losembili futsi losembili kulokuphikisana lokungaba nemiphumela yekukhetfwa kwakhe kulomnyaka lotako, naye unelikhono lelikhulu ekwetfuleni sigwebo lesitawuletfwa ngeMsombuluko.
"Sisondzele kakhulu ekubuyeleni ePacific", wasetsembisa ekupheleni kwenyanga yeNgci.
Kodvwa labanye bacwaningi bakholelwa kutsi akukavami kutsi inkantolo ikhiphe sincumo lesitawusita i-Bolivia, futsi ngisho nobe ingase ikhiphe sincumo, kutawuba netingucuko letincane.
Lomtimba weNhlangano yaMhlabuhlangene lohlala e-Netherlands ute emandla ekuniketa lendzawo yaseChile futsi utsi angeke uncume umphumela wetinkhulumiswano letingaba khona.
Kwehlulela kwalesijeziso sekugcina lokwentiwa ngemuva kwetinyanga letisitfupha kucale kulalelwa, kukhombisa kutsi lelicala belingekho melula, kusho Paz Zarate, longusosayensi waseChile lowati kakhulu ngemtsetfo wemave ngemave.
Esikhundleni sekutsi kuchubekele embili ngalelicala laseBolivia, leminyaka lemine leyengcile seyivele seyivele ibuyele emuva.
"Lenkinga yekungena elwandle yentiwa ngulabo labangubohulumende baseBolivia", kusho Zarate.
Inkhulumo lembi yaMorales yabulala bonkhe bantfu baseChile lebebasele, yabakhombisa.
I-Bolivia ne-Chile batawuchubeka nekuhlanganyela ngalelinye lilanga, kepha kutawuba matima kakhulu kutsi kuchube leminye imihlangano ngemuva kwaloku.
Lamave lamabili awakaze ashintjane ngemancusa awo kusukela nga-1962.
Umengameli wangembili Eduardo Rodriguez Veltze, ummeli wase Bolivia e-The Hague, uyencaba lendzaba yekutsi sincumo senkantolo sisheshe kakhulu.
Kutsiwa ngeMsombuluko, iBolivia itawuniketwa litfuba lelikhetsekile lekucala sikhatsi lesisha sebudlelwane neChile kanye nelitfuba lekucedza iminyaka lengu-139 yekungevani, ngekwenetisa lokufanako.
Calzadilla waphindze waphika kutsi Morales - lobekangumengameli lotsandvwa kakhulu e-Latin America - usebentisa ludzaba lwekuhamba kwakhe kuya elwandle njengentfo yekusebentisa emandla.
