John Edward: Lwati lwetiLwimi lubalulekile kubantfu bemhlaba
Sikolwa lesitifundzako eScotland siyatigcabha ngekusebenta kahle etikolweni, lokuchubeke nga 2018 ngetimphumelelo letiphakeme tekuhlola, lokuchutjwa kuphindze kuciniswe ngekuphumelela kwemuntfu ngamunye kanye nekuhlanganyela kwakhe kutemidlalo, tebuciko, umculo kanye naleminye imisebenti yemphakatsi.
Ngaletinye tikhatsi, umfundzi lofuna kufundza angafundza ku-Schools of the Future (Softa) nobe ku-Schools of the Future (Softa) nobe ku-Schools of the Future (Softa) nobe ku-Schools of the Future (Sifta).
Tikolwa letizimele tifuna kulungiselela bafundzi imfundvo lechubekako, imisebenti labayitsandzako kanye nendzawo yabo emkhatsini webantfu bemhlaba.
Njengemphakatsi lowati kutikhetsela luhlelo lwawo lwetifundvo, sibona tilwimi talamuhla tihlala titsandvwa kakhulu njengetifundvo letifundvwa emakhaya.
Nelson Mandela watsi, "Nawukhuluma nemuntfu ngelulwimi lalucondzako, uyakucondza loko".
Khuluma naye ngelulwimi lwakhe, loko kutakwenta inhlitiyo yakhe ibe nemandla.
Loku kusikhumbuta ngalokucinile kutsi singeke setsembele esiNgisini kuphela uma sifuna kwakha budlelwane lobuhle nekwetsembana nebantfu bakulamanye emave.
Ngekubuka imiphumela yekuhlola yalomnyaka, siyabona kutsi tilwimi tibe ngetulu kwato tonkhe tifundvo letiphakeme, tibe tibe netinombolo letisetulu tekuphasa etikolweni letitimele.
Kuloluhlolo, bafundzi labangu-68% batfole ticu te-A.
Emaphesenti langu-72 ebantfwana labatfola emamaki aseNyuvesi yase-Australia batfola emamaki langu-A esifundvweni sabo seSiswati, kantsi emaphesenti langu-72 ebafundzi besiJalimane, emaphesenti langu-69 ebafundzi besiFulentji, nemaphesenti langu-63 ebafundzi besiSpanishi nabo batfola emamaki langu-A.
Loku kukhombisa kutsi tikolwa letizimele eScotland tiyayisekela imfundvo yelulwimi lolwengetiwe njengelwati lolubalulekile, lokungabatisa kutsi kutawudzingeka kubantfwana kanye nakulabasha esikhatsini lesitako.
Lulwimi, njengetifundvo letitsandvwa ngulabantfu labanyenti, nyalo selutsatfwa njengetifundvo letifanana netetifundvo te-STEM (isayensi, bucwepheshe, bungcweti, nemathematics) etikolweni letitimele nakuletinye tindzawo.
Kubuta kwe-UK Commission for Employment and Skills nga-2014 kukhombisa kutsi 17% webantfu labafuna umsebenti batsi kunetinkinga tekutfola imisebenti ngoba kute bantfu labakhuluma tilwimi letinye.
Ngako-ke, lwati lwetilwimi letisive luya ngekuba lukhuni kutsi lusha lukhone kululungela umsebenti lwalo lolutako.
Njengobe kunetintfo letinyenti letifaka ekhatsi kufundza tilwimi letisandza kwentiwa, lwati lolungetiwe lolutfolakala kulelive lelibuswa ngemave lamanyenti.
Nanobe ngumuphi umsebenti umuntfu langakhetsa kuwusebentisa, kukhuluma lulwimi lunye kutawuba nemtselela lomuhle esikhatsini lesitako ngobe kukwati kusebenta imphilo yakho yonkhe.
Likhono lekuchumana ngco nebantfu labavela kulamanye emave litawubeka umuntfu lokhuluma tilwimi letinyenti kucala kunalomunye.
Ngekusho kweluhlolo lwe-YouGov lolwentiwe ngetulu kwe-4 000 yebantfu baseBrithani nga-2013, emaphesenti lamashumi lasikhombisa nesikhombisa abengalati lulwimi lolwengetiwe ngalokwenele kutsi bangakwati kuchumana, kantsi siFulentji bekunguyona kuphela lulwimi lwe-digit, emaphesenti lalishumi nesihlanu.
Kungako-ke kubalulekile kutsi bantfwana lamuhla batsatse sikhatsi sekufundza tilwimi.
Kwati tilwimi letinyenti, ikakhulukati tilwimi letisemnotfweni losatfutfuka, kungenta bantfwana babe nelitfuba lelikahle lekutfola umsebenti lokahle.
E-Scotland, sikolwa ngasinye sehlukile uma kuziwa elulwimini lolusemtsetfweni.
Letinye tifundvo titawugcila etilwimini tesimanje, kantsi letinye titawutfola tifundvo letitsite ngetilwimi letitawubaluleka kakhulu e-UK nga-2020, njengesiMandarin nesiJapane.
Nobe ngabe ngumuphi umgomo wemntfwana wakho, kutawutsi njalo-nje kube khona tilwimi letimbalwa langatikhetsela tona etikolweni letizimele, letinemfundziso lefundziswa ngulabo labati kahle lulwimi.
Tikolo taseScotland letitimele tinemgomo wekufundzisa bantfwana ngendlela letawubasita kutsi baphumelele ngisho nome ngabe babhekene netimo letitsite.
Kulomhlaba lesiphila kuwo, kute longaphika kutsi ngetilwimi, kuhlangana kwemabhizinisi emhlaba wonkhe, kubalulekile kulelive, futsi loko kufanele kuvele emfundvweni.
Tilwimi talamuhla kumele tibhekwe njengekuchumana lokuchubekako emkhatsini webantfu.
Tikolwa letitimele titawuchubeka nekuniketa loku kukhetsa, kwehlukahlukana kanye nekuhlakanipha kubantfu labasha baseScotland.
Kufanele kutsi bakwente kahle.
