Umengameli Donald Trump ucalise umbutsano wakhe wekukhetsa lamuhla eWheeling, eWest Virginia.
Lena yintfo yekucala kuletinkhulumo letisihlanu taTrump letihlelelwe kuhlangana kuleliviki lelitako lokufaka ekhatsi kuvakashela tindzawo letifana neTennessee kanye neMississippi.
Njengobe alindzeleke kutsi akhetse kutsi ngubani lotawugcwalisa sikhundla seNkantolo lePhakeme, Trump uhlela kukhulisa kusekela kwakhe lukhetfo lwekhatsi kwemnyaka lolutako njengoba emaRephabliki asengotini yekulahlekelwa ligunya lawo ekushayweni kweMkhandlu weTifundza ngemuva kwekuvota ngaNovemba.
Ngusiphi sikhatsi sembutfo wa Trump eWest Virginia lamuhla kusihlwa, futsi ungawubuka njani ku-internet?
Umhlangano waTrump eWheeling, West Virginia, uhlelelwe kutsi ube ngilo lelilanga kusihlwa ngensimbi yesikhombisa ntsambama, ngeliSontfo, Septhemba 29, 2018.
Ungayibukela le-Trump rally e-West Virginia ngephansi kwalengoma lengcondvomshini ku-YouTube.
Kwatsi nakusondzela sikhatsi sekukhuluma, kwavele kwavela kutsi ema-agentshi etemtsetfo e-United States asebentisa imitsetfo yawo kute asekele emacala abo.
Kodvwa inhloso lenkhulu yalembutsano yekuhlangana ngukutsi kusite iRiphabhulikhi yente lokuhle kakhulu elukhetfweni lwangaNovemba.
Ngako-ke, likomidi laMengameli Trump, litjele Reuters kutsi, lemigubho yalengcenye yalenyanga yentiwa kute "kuniketwe emandla emavolontiya kanye nebasekeli njengobe emalunga e-Republican alwela kuvikela nekukhulisa bukhulu bawo e-Senate kanye nase-House of Representatives".
"Kuhlola iKhongresesi yintfo lebalulekile eluhlelweni lwakhe lokwenta umengameli ahambe aye kumave lamanyenti njengobe singena esikhatsini semkhankaso", kusho sikhulumi selicembu laTrump, lesete kutibonakalisa.
Kubekelwe eWesbanco Arena eWheeling, umbutsano wasebusuku bebangahlanganisa bantfu base-Ohio nasePennsylvania kanye nekubamba kubaluleka kwe-Pittsburgh, ngekusho kwe-West Virginia Metro News.
Umsebenti waMandela we-Washington, N.Y. utawuba wekucala kulenyanga kutsi Trump avakashele eWest Virginia, live lapho ancoba khona ngemaphesenti langetulu kwa-40 nga-2016.
Trump wetama kusita Patrick Morrissey, umholi welicembu le-Republican, lotawutfola sikhundla seSenethi sase-West Virginia, longakhombisi kahle ekulinganisweni kwebavoti.
"Akusikahle kutsi uMengameli ete atewuphakamisa lizinga lakhe lekuvota", kusho Simon Haeder, losati sesayensi yetepolitiki eNyuvesi yaseWest Virginia, ngekusho kwaReuters.
