Bafundzi base-Harvard bafundziswa kutsi bangatiphumuta njani
Ikhosi lensha leseyivele ivele ku Nyuvesi yase Harvard kulomnyaka ihlose kwenta bafundzi kutsi balale kakhulu kute bacedze lendlela leyandzile yekutsandza kufundza lokwenta bantfu bacitse busuku bonkhe basebentisa i-caffeine.
Lomunye umfundzi wetemfundvo lephakeme waveta kutsi bafundzi labasemayunivesithi lasemhlabeni wonkhe bavame kungawati emaciniso labalulekile ngekutiphatsa.
Charles Czeisler, longuphrofesa wetekwelapha ngekulala eHarvard Medical School kanye nalonguchwepheshe eBrigham and Women's Hospital, wente luhlelo lolutsite lolungilo kuphela lolusebenta ngalendlela eMelika.
Kantsi futsi waphefumulelwa kutsi acale lesifundvo ngemuva kwekuniketwa yinkhulumo yakhe lemayelana nemiphumela yekungalali kahle nawufundza.
 Ekugcineni, kwefika intfombatana kimi, yatsi:  "Kungani ningitjela loku nyalo, kulomnyaka wami wekucala?
Watsi kute umuntfu lowake wamtjela kutsi liphupho libaluleke kangakanani, loku kwangimangalisa kakhulu, " washo njalo kuThe Telegraph.
Sifundvo lesetfulwe kwekucala kulomnyaka, sifundzisa bafundzi kutsi indlela lekahle yekulala yenta ncono timfundvo tabo, imitsi kanye nemphilo yabo.
Paul Barreira, longuthishela wetemphilo eHarvard Medical School kanye nalokhokhela umsebenti wetemphilo enyuvesi, utsi leyonyuvesi yancuma kufundzisa bantfu labanenkinga yekulala kakhulu kuleliviki.
Lenkhulumo lefundvwa ngelihora linye inemisebenti leminingi lelandzelanako.
Kulesinye sicephu, kunesitfombe selikamelo lelisendlini yekulala, bafundzi bacocwa ngetitja telikhofi, emakhethini, ticatfulo kanye netincwadzi kute bati kabanti ngemiphumela yekunatsa ligwayi kanye nekukhanya, kanye nemiphumela yekungalali kahle emicimbini yetemidlalo kanye nekubaluleka kwekwenta luhlelo lwekuya embhedzeni.
Kantsi, kwesibili, bantfu labatsintsekako batjelwa kutsi kungalali sikhatsi lesidze kungakhulisa ematfuba ekushaywa yinhlitiyo, kuhlushwa sifo semsheko, kucindzeteleka kanye nemdlavuza.
Kantsi futsi, ibalave lelikhona linetimphawu letihambisanako leticondzisa bafundzi kutsi bacabange ngemihambo yabo ya onkhe malanga.
Siyati kutsi loku angeke kugucule indlela bafundzi labenta ngayo.
Kodvwa sicabanga kutsi banelilungelo lekwati  njengobe nawe unelilungelo lekwati imiphumela yekubhema yakho kutemphilo", kusho Prof. Czeisler.
Watsi: "Lisiko lekutikhukhumeta ngekutsi 'siphapheme ebusuku' lisekhona, kodvwa bucwepheshe lobusha kanye nekucindzeteleka lokukhulu kwebafundzi kwenta kube matima kutsi bantfu balale sikhatsi lesidze.
Kulala lokwanele kanye nekulala lokusezingeni lelisetulu kufanele kube yintfo yemfundzi levikela kucindzeteleka, kukhatsateka kanye nekucindzeteleka, ngisho nekukhuluphala, ngobe kungalali kwenta ingcondvo ihambe ngendlela yekungalali kahle, ngako-ke ihlala ilambile.
Raymond So, umfundzi weminyaka lelishumi nakune budzala, wetemvelo yemakhemikhali wase California, wasita Profesa Cheisler ekwakheni lelikharikhulamu ngemuva kwekuya kulelinye lalamacembu akhe ngemnyaka wakhe wekucala eHarvard.
Utsi leliklasi limvulele emehlo futsi lamenta kutsi afune kutsi lomsebenti wentiwa ngelizinga lelihle kakhulu.
Kulesinye sigaba, litsemba lekutsi bonkhe labafuna kufundza baphotfwe tifundvo letisezingeni leliphakeme batawucelwa kutsi babhalise kulesinye sifundvo ngaphambi kwekutsi bangenele kulesinye sikhungo.
Profesa Czeisler utjele bafundzi kutsi bacabange ngekusebentisa i-alamu ngesikhatsi sekulala nesekusukuma, kanye nekunaka imiphumela lemibi "yekukhanya lokuluhlata sasibhakabhaka" lokukhishwa kukhombisa kwe-elekthronikhi kanye nekukhanyisa kwe-LED, lokungaphatamisa umjikeleto wemalanga, lokungabangela kutsi umuntfu abe nenkinga yekulala.
