Mengo washaya emaminithi lasikhombisa ngaphambi kwesikhatsi sekwehlukanisa, kantsi licembu lelingakacabangi le-Rangers alizange lisondzele ngisho nasendzaweni yekulinganisa.
Njengobe iRanger seyifike endzaweni yesitfupha, iLivingston seyifike endzaweni yesitsatfu, ngemuva kweHibernian ngemgomo munye.
Emadvodza lamasotja abese ayahlangana netinkinga letengetiwe ngemuva kwekutsi umcashi Calum Spence atfole lusito ngesikhatsi aphutfwa ngemcibisholo.
Gerrard wente lushintjo loluphelele kulelicembu lelatfola umhlomelo ku-Ayr futsi lelagcina selingene emidlalweni ye-Betfred Cup.
Ngakulolunye luhlangotsi, Holt bekatimisele ngekutsatsa labashayeli beLivingston labangu-11 lebebatfole emaphuzu lamabili eHearts kuleliviki leliphelile, futsi bekatakujabulela kubona indlela lelicembu lakhe lebeliceceshe ngayo licindzetela labo lebelibamelene nabo kuto tonkhe tinhlangotsi.
I-Rangers beyingenabo lobunjinga, kepha Livingston bekenta lokuncono ngesikhatsi sakhe.
Besekusele kancane kutsi bacedze umgomo wabo ngemizuzu lemibili ngemuva kwekutsi Meng ashaya ligoli lekucala ku-under-the-field, lokwenta Scott Pittman kutsi ahambe ku-Allman McGregor, kepha umdlali wasenkhundleni wasebentisa litfuba lelikhulu futsi wacosha lidzili lelisedvute.
Sibhamu lesinemandla saKeaghan Jacobs saphindze safika kuKaputeni Craig Halkett, kodvwa umlingani wakhe ngekusekela, Alan Lithgow, wakhona kushaya kancane nje, wabese uyahamba.
I-Rangers yakhona kutsatsa sikhundla, kepha umdlalo wabo wekugcina waveta litsemba kunekukholwa emidlalweni yabo.
Alfredo Morelos bekati kutsi kufanele atfole iphenikhodi ngemizuzu lengu-15 ngesikhatsi yena naSteven Lawless bashayisana, kepha lijaji, Steven Thomson, walahla sicelo saColombia.
I-Rangers yaba nelitfuba lekubhema kabili ekucaleni kwethemu, kepha umgadli we-Ibrox Liam Kelly, ngekushesha wavikela kubhema kwaLassane Coulibaly ngekukhanda, wabese uvikela kushaya kwa-Ovie Ejaria.
Nanobe umgomo wekucala waLivingstone emaminithini langu-34 bewungakhombisi kahle indlela lebalwe ngayo, kodvwa kute umuntfu longaphika kutsi bekumfanele, ngenca yemsebenti wakhe.
Labangani futsi bebangaba nemandla ekuhlasela lokukhululekile kwaJacob.
Scott Arfield wehluleka kuphendvula ngesikhatsi Declan Gallagher anika Scott Robinson lebekabindzile, futsi wakhetsa Mengu ngempumelelo.
Gerrard waphendvula ngekusebentisa Ryan Kent esikhundleni saCoulibaly futsi loko kwavele kwaholela ekudleni kwaMorelos, kodvwa Kelly lomangalisako wavele wavala indlela.
Noma kunjalo, Livingston wachubeka nekwenta tivakashi takhe kutsi tidlale ngendlela letiyitsandzako, ngetibhola letindze teLithgow neHalkett.
Ecenjini, Holt bekanematfuba lamanyenti ekutsi atsatse indzawo yakhe, kepha McGregor wavikela Jacobs, kwatsi Lithgow wacala ngekumphosa inhloko yakhe.
Glenn Middleton, longasinye se-Rangers, wacela kutsi kukhishwe lelinye liphenathi ngemuva kwekubambana na Jacobs, kepha Thomson akazange aphindze atiphendvule.
