Umengameli waseMelika, Donald Trump, ngeLwesitsatfu, ukhulume ngekukhokhela kweliphephandzaba laseChina Daily, lelifakwa ku-Des Moines Register, liphephandzaba lelihamba embili e-Iowa, ngemuva kwekusola i-China ngekuhlanganyela elukhetfweni lwe-US Congress lolutakwentiwa ngeLweti 6, intfo i-China lephika kutsi ayikho.
