Umkhumbi lomusha wemphi wemaJalimane sewulindze kutsi ukhuphuke
Umkhumbi wemphi lomusha wase-German Navy bekufanele kutsi ufike ngemnyaka wa-2014 kutsi utsatse indzawo yemikhumbi yemphi yesikhatsi seMphi yeMshana, kepha angeke ufike sikhatsi lesidze lokungenani umnyaka ngenca yekusebenta kabi kwetintfo kanye nekubita kakhulu, kwabika tindzaba takulendzawo.
Kukhishwa kwemkhumbi iRheinland-Pfalz, umkhumbi loholako esigabeni semikhumbi lemisha yaseBaden-Wuerttemberg, sekubekwe eceleni kuze kube yinyanga yekucala ya 2019, ngekusho kweliphephandzaba iDie Zeit, lelicashunwe ngumkhulumeli wembutfo wemphi.
Lomkhumbi bekulindzeleke kutsi ujoyine lisotja lemkhumbi ngemnyaka wa 2014, kepha tinkinga tekutfulwa kwemikhumbi taletsa tinkinga kulomsebenti.
Imikhumbi lemine yemasotja aseBaden-Wuerttemberg leyalelwa nga-2007 itawugucula imikhumbi yemasotja aseBremen.
Ngekusho kwalomculu, itawuba nesibhamu lesinemandla, luhlu lwetilimato letihlasela emoyeni kanye nemikhumbi, kanjalo naletinye tindlela tekungabonakali, njengekunciphisa i-radar, i-infrared kanye nekusebentisa imisindvo.
Letinye tintfo letibalulekile tifaka ekhatsi sikhatsi lesidze sekulondvolota - kumele kukhone kutsi kususwe letigadla letinsha kungakapheli iminyaka lemibili ngaphandle kwekubuyela emuva kumakhaya ato.
Njengobe bekusolo kuchutjwa sikhatsi, loku kusho kutsi lemikhumbi lemikhulu yesimanje, lebeyifanele kutsi isite iJalimane kutsi ikhone kuhambisa emabutfo ayo kulamanye emave, beseyivele iphelelwe sikhatsi nasekucala kusetjentiswa, kusho i-Zeit.
Lelicembu le-F125 lelahlukako labese lifikile etindzabeni ngemnyaka lophelile, lapho khona lisotja lemkhumbi le-German Navy lavele lalela kutsi lihambe futsi labuyisela lomkhumbi e-Blohm & Voss, eHamburg.
Bekukwekucala ngca kutsi sikebhe semkhumbi sibuyiselwe kumcashi waso ngemuva kwekwetfulwa.
Kuncane lokwatiwako ngetizatfu tekutsi kungani lesigubhu sibuyiselwe emuva, kepha emajaji aseJalimane akhuluma ngetinkinga letinkhulu tekusebenta kwasofthiwe kanye netintfo tekusebenta kwaso letingabangela kutsi sikebhe singasebenti nangabe singabekwa kutsi sisebente.
Tinkinga tetinhlelo letisetjentiswako betibalulekile ngobe lemikhumbi yeBaden-Wuerttemberg itawube icondziswa ngemadvodza langu-120 - lokungulokungaba nguhhafu wenombolo yebantfu lebebasebenta ngemikhumbi lemidzala ye-Bremen.
Kantsi futsi, lemikhumbi beyimcoka kakhulu, futsi loko bekwenta kube matima kutsi isebentise emandla ayo.
Lomkhumbi lonemathani langu 7000 i "Rheinland-Pfalz" kucatjangwa kutsi unesisindvo lesiningi ngalokuphindvwe kabili kunemkhumbi walolu hlobo lowentiwa ngemaJalimane eMphini yeMhlaba yeBili.
Ngetulu kwetintfo letingasebenti kahle, tindleko tekucedza umsebenti, kufaka ekhatsi kuceceshwa kwebasebenti, nako kuyaceka.
Kutsiwa lemali leyakhokhwa yenyuka yaba ngu-€3 billion (R1 billion) nayikhuphuka nayikhuphuka nayisiya ku-$2.2 billion (R3 billion).
Tinkinga letiphatselene nemikhumbi yemikhumbi lemisha tibonakala tikhulu kakhulu ngekulandzela tecwayiso letisandza kwentiwa tekutsi emandla aseJalimane elwandle ayanyamalala.
Ekucaleni kwalomnyaka, Hans-Peter Bartels, umengameli welikomidi letemphi lePhalamende yaseJalimane, wavuma kutsi leNavy "inetikhali letingahle tisetjentiswe".
Lesikhulu satsi lenkinga ikhule ngekuhamba kwesikhatsi, ngoba imikhumbi lemidzala beyikhulunyiswa, futsi bekungekho imikhumbi leminye leyatfolwa.
Wativa buhlungu ngekutsi kute ngisho yinye yemahhashi lasetulu eBaden-Wuerttemberg lahlangana neMikhumbi yeMikhumbi.
Sikhwama savelonkhe semabhuku silalela imphilo lemfihlo yalaboshako
Lucwaningo lolwentiwe endzaweni lenkhulu yaseThamenland, eScotland, luhlose kubona kutsi bomshakatsi basebentisa njani lendzawo kute batfole kudla.
Lokwatfolwa kulolucwaningo kulindzeleke kutsi kusikhanyisele kakhulu ngekutiphatsa kwaletilwane letindizako letinemtimba longetulu, kuphindze kusite ekulondvoloteni tintfo letingaba lusito esikhatsini lesitako.
Lolucwaningo lolwentiwe bososayensi labaphuma ku-National Trust of Scotland, batawulandzela emalulwane lasemantini kanye nemalulwane lasemkhatsini, i-Sopranella pipistrella, kanye nemalulwane lamnyama lanematinyo lamadze kanye nemalulwane lasemantini, i-Daubenton, e-Inverewe Gardens eWester Ross.
Imishini lekhetsekile yekutsatsa titfombe itawubekwa etindzaweni letibalulekile letisemkhatsini walesigodzi kute kulandzelwe umsebenti wemabhambu ngesikhatsi sawo.
Basebenti nemavolontiya e-NHS batawenta luhlolo loluhambako ngekusebentisa bomshayeli bemikhono.
Luhlolo lolucophelwe lwemininingwane lebhalwe kulelibhokisi litawutfola kutsi leligwaja lifane kangakanani kubengulabo labamshayelako, nekutsi ngutiphi tinhlobo letehlukene taloluhlobo.
Ngemuva kwaloko, kutawentiwa ema-habitat map kanye nemibiko kute kwakhiwe sitfombe lesicwebetelako setindlela tekutiphatsa kwato letisezingeni lendzawo.
Rob Dewar, umeluleki wetekongiwa kwemvelo eNTS, unethemba lekutsi imiphumela yetinhlolovo takhe itokhombisa kutsi ngutiphi tindzawo letibalulekile kubelulwane nekutsi luhlobo lolutsite lusebentisa njani.
Lolwati lutawusita kutfola tinzuzo tekwenta umsebenti wekunakekela indzawo, njengekwakha indzawo yekuhlanyela, nekutsi nguyiphi indlela lekahle yekugcina emahlatsi emabhamuti kanye naletinye tilwane letihlobene nawo.
Ema batmbe ase Scotland nase UK ancipha kakhulu ngeminyaka lelikhulu leyengcile.
Tintfo letisatfutfukako letitfolwa emantini tifaka imfuyo yabo engotini ngekwakha nekutfutfukisa, lokutsintsa emagungumence kanye nekulahleka kwendzawo.
Tintfo letihambisana nemoya kanye nekukhanyiswa nako kungaletsa tingoti, letifaka ekhatsi emaphepha lanamatselako kanye nekusebentisa emakhemikhali nakwakhiwa kwetakhiwo, kanye nekuhlaselwa yimikhuhlane.
Emalulwane akaboni kahle.
Nobe kunjalo, ngenca yemkhuba wato wekutingela ebusuku, tindlebe tato tilusito kakhulu kunemehlo ekubambeni kudla.
Tisebentisa indlela lephakeme yekubona tintfo letincane letiphilako kute tibe netintfo letingaba ngumkhuba wato.
I-NTS, lebhekele takhiwo temlandvo letingetulu kwa-270 kanye netingadze letibalulekile letingu-38 kanye nemhlaba longemahektha la-76 000 eveni lonkhe, ibatsatsa kakhulu ema-batter.
Kunebantfu labaceceshiwe labacishe babe lishumi labenta umsebenti wekuhlola, kuhlolisisa indzawo yekuhlala, futsi ngalesinye sikhatsi ngisho nekusindzisa.
Lenhlangano yaze yasungula indzawo yekucala kanye neyodvwa yemaBhatati eScotland, endzaweni yaseThreave eDumfriese naseGalloway, lapho kuhlala khona tilwane letisiphohlongo kuletilwane letilishumi taseScotland.
Umphatsi welikhaya, David Thompson, utsi lendzawo ililungelo labo.
"Lapha eThreave sinendzawo lenkhulu yemalulwane", washo njalo.
Sineyakhe imimango lendzala, sihlanyele tihlahla letindzala, futsi sinato tonkhe tintfo letilungile.
Kodvwa kunalokunyenti lokungalatiwa ngema orchid, ngako lesikwentako lapha naletinye tindzawo letitfolakala emabhululohweni kutasisita kutsi sicondze kancono kutsi yini ledzingekako kutsi tilwane tikhone kuchubeka nekuphila.
Uphindze agcizelele kutsi kubalulekile kutsi kubukwe emabhokisi lapho kunemagundvwane khona, ngobe nakungaba nesicumbi semagundvwane, umhlambi wemagundvwane lomncane ungabulala emabhubesi lamakhulu lamane kanye nemazinyane, lokungaholela ekubhujisweni kwemmango wonkhe.
Emabhatsimvu tilwane letivikelekile futsi akuvunyelwe kutsi ubulale, uphatse kabi, uphatse kabi noma ubhubhise tilwane letihlala kuwo.
Elizabeth Ferrell, losisebenti seSikhungo Sekulondvolota Emalulwane eScotland, ukhutsate sive kutsi sihlanganyele futsi sisite.
Watsi, "Kunyenti kakhulu lokusamele sikufundze ngemabhungane etfu, futsi asiyati indlela leminingi yetinhlobo tetfu letitfutfuka ngayo".
