#Brexit: UK itawuhlaba umkhosi ngekulahlekelwa bakhiciti beTimoto
I-UK "itawuhlale ilila" uma ilahlekelwa sigaba sayo sekuba ngumholi wemhlaba ekwakhiweni kwetimoto ngemuva kwe-Brexit, kusho i-Secretary yeBusiness Greg Clark.
Wengeta ngekutsi "kuyakhatsateka" loko lokwashiwo yiToyota UK ku-BBC - uma iBrithani ishiya i-EU ngaphandle kwesivumelwano kutsi itawuvala sikhatsi sekukhicita e-Burnstone, edvute nase-Derby.
"Sidzinga sivumelwano", kusho Clark.
Umkhicito wetimoto waseJapan utsi kubambeleleka kwekwehla kwemincele uma iBexit ingasebenti kungaholela ekulahlekeni kwemisebenti.
Sikhungo seToyota eAuris naseAvensis eBurston sikhicite timoto leticishe tibe ngu-150 000 ngemnyaka lophelile, 90% wakhona lowakhishelwa kulamanye emave e-European Union.
"Ngumbono wami kutsi uma iNgilandi ishiya i-EU ekupheleni kwaMashi, sitawubona kuphelelwa sikhatsi kwekukhicita kwasemkhakheni wetfu", kusho Marvin Cooke, umenenja jikelele weToyota eBurnsdon.
Labanye bakhiciti bema-U.K. labafaka ekhatsi i-Honda, i-BMW kanye ne-Jaguar Land Rover bakhulume ngekwesaba kutsi batawuhweba njani emave langesheya uma i-UK ishiya i-EU ngaphandle kwesivumelwano.
BMW, sibonelo, utsi batawuvala imboni yabo lencane e-Oxford inyanga ngemuva kwe-Brexit.
Lokukhatsateka lokukhulu nguloko lokushiwo bakhi betimoto kutsi kungaba yingoti kulesitolo sekutsenga nangabe i-Brexit ingentiwa.
I-Toyota's production line isebenta nge 'just-on-time' lapho tincenye tifika njalo ngemizuzu lengu-37 kusuka e-UK nase-EU kuniketela ngetimoto letentiwe ngendlela.
Uma i-UK ishiya i-EU ngaphandle kwesivumelwano nga-March 29, kungahle kube nekuhlukunyetwa emnceleni lokungaholela ekubambeni kwesikhatsi kanye nasetintfweni letitfolakala ngekutiphilisa.
Bekungeke kwenteke kutsi iToyota igcine timphahla tekusebenta emalanga lambalwa esakhiweni sayo sase Derbyshire, kusho inkampani, ngako-ke umkhicito bewutawuyekela.
Umnumzane Clark watsi luhlelo lwe "Chequers" loluhlelwe nguTheresa May lwebudlelwane besikhatsi lesitako ne-EU "luhlelwe kahle kute luvimbe lokugada kwemasango".
"Kufanele sibe nesivumelwano. Sifuna kufinyelela sivumelwano lesincono lesitawenta kutsi, njengobe ngitsi, singagcini nje ngekunambitseka kwemphumelelo yetfu yanyalo, kodvwa siphindze sisebentise lelitfuba", washo etfule enkhulumeni ye-BBC Radio 4 namuhla.
"Sibonelo, hhayi iToyota kuphela kodvwa naletinye timboni, kutsi kufanele sikhone kuchubeka naloko lokwenteke ngemphumelelo lenkhulu kulesikhatsi lesengcile".
I-Toyota ayizange ikhone kusho kutsi kukhicitwa kwayo kutawumiswa sikhatsi lesingakanani, kepha yacaphela kutsi esikhatsini lesidze, letindleko letengetiwe titawucindzetela umkhicito wayo kutsi uncintisane nemakethe futsi ekugcineni kunciphise imisebenti.
Peter Tsouvallaris, lobekasebente eBurnstone iminyaka lengu 24 futsi nalengumengameli we Unite union kulefemu, utsi emalunga ayo bekakhatsatekile kakhulu: "Ngekubona kwami, uma lemisebenti seyivaliwe, angeke iphindze ibuye.
Sikhulumi sahulumende satsi: "Kufanele sibeke luhlelo lolucondzile futsi lolunemandla lwebudlelwane betfu ne-EU esikhatsini lesitako".
Kubekwa kwaTrump emhlanganweni naRosenstein kungahlehliswa, kusho iWhite House
Umhlangano lobaluleke kakhulu wa Donald Trump neSekela laMshushisi Jikelele Rod Rosenstein ungahle "ubekwe eceleni ngeliviki" njengoba umzabalazo uchubeka ngekukhetfwa kwa Brett Kavanaugh, i-White House itsi ngeLisontfo.
Rosenstein ubuka umsebenti welihhovisi lelikhetsekile laRobert Mueller, lophenya emacala ekutimbandzakanya kweRussia elukhetfweni, budlelwano emkhatsini webalekeleli baTrump kanye neRussia, kanye nekuphatamiseka kwebulungiswa ngumengameli.
Kubamba nobe kungasebenti kwelihhovisi lebu-SAG, nekubekwa engotini kweMnu Mueller, sekusitsikameti lesitsatsa tinyanga eWashington.
Ekucaleni kwenyanga, iNew York Times ibike kutsi Rosenstein ucoce ngekusebentisa i-microphone kute abhale inkhulumo yakhe na Trump kanye nelikhono lekususa umengameli ngekwelilungelo lakhe lekuba ngumengameli.
Rosenstein akavumanga kutsi bekunguye.
