Ngenca yekuhluleka kwechumana, tisebenti tekusita bantfu betehluleka kutfola imininingwane levela esifundzeni sase Donggale, indzawo lesenyakatfo yePalu lesele dvute nelikhaya lalesitfombe lesingu 7.5.
Bantfu labangetulu kwa-16 000 bacosha tindzawo tabo ngemuva kwesehlakalo lesenteka ePalau.
Nankha lamanye emaciniso labalulekile ngePalu naseDonggali, esichingini saseSulawesi:
I-Palu ilidolobha lelikhulu lesifundza sase Sulawesi, lelisemkhatsini weligumbi lelisemkhatsini kanye neligumbi lelisemkhatsini.
Lelidolobha beligubha iminyaka yalo lengu-40 ngesikhatsi sehlelwa kutamatama kwemhlaba kanye ne-tsunami.
Donggala yindzawo lechubekako lechubekela ngaselugwini lolungetulu kwemakhilomitha lamakhulu lamatsatfu (180 km) enyakatfo-nshonalanga yesichingi sase Sulawesi.
Lesigodzi lesingaphansi kwesifundza, besinabantfu labacagele kutsi babe ngu 299,200 nga 2017.
Umnotfo weSifundza saseCentral Sulawesi, ikakhulukati i-Donggala, ucondziswa kutingela kanye nekulima.
Timayini te nickel nato tibalulekile kulesigodzi, kepha tivame kutfolakala eMorowali, lemelele Sulawesi.
I-Palu ne-Donggala betihlaselwe ti-tsunami tikhatsi letinyenti kuleminyaka lelikhulu leyengcile, ngekusho kwe-Indonesia Disaster Mitigation Agency.
Nga-1938, i-tsunami yabulala bantfu labangetulu kwa-200, futsi yabhidlita emakhaya lamakhulu aseDonggala.
I-Tsunami yahlasela i-Western Donggala nga-1996 kwashona bantfu labasitfupha.
I-Indonesia itfolakala endzaweni lekutsiwa yi-Pacific Seismic Ring of Fire futsi ihlala igadla kutamatama kwemhlaba.
Letinye tetehlakalo letinkhulu temonakalo wetanyakatane kanye nemitsamo yemanti kuleminyaka lembalwa leyengcile:
2004: Kutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu elugwini lolungaseningizimu ye-Indonesia esifundzeni sase-Aceh lesise-North Sumatra ngaDecember 26, kwabangela kutsi kube ne-tsunami leyasakateka emaveni la-14, yabulala bantfu labangu-226,000 elugwini loluselugwini lwe-Indian Ocean, lokungetulu kwehhafu yabo lebeyi-Aceh.
2005: Kuhlokoma lokukhulu kwelitulu kwahlasela lwandle lolungaseningizimu yeSumatra ekupheleni kwa-March kanye nasekucaleni kwa-April.
Emakhulu ebantfu bafa esichingini sase Nias eceleni kwelwandle lwase Sumatra.
2006: Kutamatama kwemhlaba lokunemandla langu 6.8 lokunemandla lalishumi nakubili kwagadla ngaseningizimu ye Java, lokuyindzawo lenkhulu kunato tonkhe tive tase Indonesia, kwabangela tsunami leyakhukhula ngaseningizimu yelugwini futsi yabulala bantfu labanga-700.
2009: Kutamatama kwemhlaba lokunemandla la 7.6 kuhlasele lidolobha lasePadang, lelidolobha lelikhulu lesifundza saseSumatra leseNshonalanga.
Bantfu labangetulu kwa-1 100 bafa.
2010: Kutamatama kwemhlaba lokungu-7.5 nge-magnitude kwashaya Mentawai Island, lesedvute neSumatra, kwabangela tsunami longaba ngemamitha lalishumi, lowabhubhisa emadolobhana lamanyenti wabulala nebantfu labangaba ngu-300.
2016: Kutamatama kwemhlaba lokungazange kube nemtselela lomkhulu kubhubhise indzawo yasePidie Jaya lese-Acehu, lokwabangela kutsi kubhujiswe tindzawo futsi bantfu besaba kakhulu, lokuyintfo leyakhumbuta bantfu ngekutamatama kwemhlaba lokwabulala bantfu labanyenti kanye ne-tsunami yanga-2004.
Akukenteki tsunami ngalesikhatsi, kodvwa bantfu labangetulu kwa-100 babulawa nakugadla takhiwo.
Nga-2018: Kutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu kuhlasela sihlenge sase-Indonesia i-Lombok, kubulala bantfu labangetulu kwa-500, ikakhulukati enyakatfo yalesichingi.
Lokudvuma kwelitulu kubhubhise tinkhulungwane tetakhiwo, futsi tinkhulungwane tetivakashi tibhajwe kwesikhashana.
